              Our Vision
            </p>
            <br>
            <p class="subtitle" style="color:black; font-weight:400">
              In the City of New York, we recognize that deaths and serious injuries in traffic are not inevitable "accidents", 
              but preventable crashes that can be ended through engineering, enforcement, and education. 
              Vision Zero is a movement known internationally that aims to eliminate the number of fatalities and life-threatening injuries in car accidents. 
              Utilizing the NYPD Car Crashes dataset, our team has built an API for developers who want to make the city's street safer for any kind of road users.
            </p>
          </div>
